reviewText: Beautifully written boo:  another hit by Sharon Costello.
EXCELLENT, GREAT INSTRUCTIONS.  CAN't WAIT TO START WET FELTING
The best, I really love this DVD and can not wait to really use it in my work with Felting.

This is a fairly simple dvd showing step-by-step how to make the one project pictured and not too much else. It is very good if you have no experience in felting. I was slightly disappointed, but I did learn a few things that I can use.
